Package: austin
Type: Package
Title: A package for doing things with words
Version: 0.2
Date: 2012-01-05
Author: Will Lowe
Maintainer: Will Lowe <will.lowe@uni-mannheim.de>
Description: Doing things with words currently means scaling documents on a
    presumed underlying dimension on the basis of word frequencies and heroic
    assumptions about language generation.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
    numDeriv,
    Matrix
License: GPL
Collate:
    'austin.R'
    'engines.R'
    'uncertainty.R'
    'wfm.R'
    'wordfish.R'
    'wordscores.R'
